videos.description: Gordon Hayward drops a nice bounce pass to Daniel Theis in the lane to flush a two-handed jam to extend the Celtics' lead to 22-17 over the Heat.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Hayward sets up Theis for the easy dunk) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hayward sets up Theis for the easy dunk

videos.description: Goran Dragic drives and tosses an alle-oop pass to Bam Adebayo, who finishes at the rim with a two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Dragic lobs to Bam for the slam) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dragic lobs to Bam for the slam

videos.description: Jayson Tatum runs through Jae Crowder on the fast break and takes flight to hammer home an emphatic one-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum bodies Crowder for the emphatic slam) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum bodies Crowder for the emphatic slam

videos.description: Gordon Hayward comes up with the steal and outlets to Jayson Tatum, who goes up to finish with a dunk, drawing the foul for the and-1 in the process.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum takes flight for and-1 finish) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum takes flight for and-1 finish

videos.description: Tyler Herro drives deep into the paint and puts up an acrobatic layup between two Celtics defenders that spins off the top of the backboard and in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Herro makes acrobatic layup through 2 defenders) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herro makes acrobatic layup through 2 defenders

videos.description: Kemba Walker breaks down the Celtics' Game 3 win over the Heat, saying they learned from their first two losses in the series.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Kemba: Celtics learned from first two losses to Heat) 2020/9/19 SVP
